gujarati.context:
Here is a summary of the couplet:

My life force now dwells elsewhere, so I won't seek to disturb your peaceful gathering; 
The saint advises me, dear brother, that it's time for you to settle into meditation.

transliteration.context:
Here is a summary of the Gujarati couplet in English:

Send your message swiftly as a messenger, and get the reply quickly; 
This life belongs to you, do what you like, for everything else belongs to me.
